e (Long Island Rail Road)|Main Line]], [[Port Washington Branch]]<br />'''[[NJ Transit Rail Operations|NJ Transit]]:''' [[North Jersey Coast Line]], [[Northeast Corridor Line]], [[Gladstone Branch]], [[Montclair-Boonton Line]], [[Morristown Line]]<br />'''[[New York City Subway|NYC Subway]]:''' {{NYCS Broadway-Seventh|complex=y}}, {{NYCS Eighth south|complex=y}}, {{NYCS Herald Square|complex=end}}<br />'''[[MTA Regional Bus Operations|NYC Transit buses]]'''<br/>'''[[PATH (rail system)|PATH]]:''' [[Hoboken\u201333rd Street]], [[Journal Square\u201333rd Street]], [[Journal Square\u201333rd Street (via Hoboken)]]\n|-\n| rowspan=3|[[New Jersey]]||[[Newark, New Jersey|Newark]]||[[Pennsylvania Station (Newark)|Newark Penn Station]]||'''[[Amtrak]]:''' {{lnl|Amtrak|Northeast Regional}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Cardinal}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Carolinian}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Crescent}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Keystone Service}},  {{lnl|Amtrak|Palmetto}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Pennsylvanian}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Silver Meteor}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Silver Star}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Vermonter}}<br>'''[[NJ Transit Rail Operations|NJ Transit]]:''' [[Newark Light Rail#Newark City Subway|Newark City Subway]], [[Newark Light Rail#Newark Light Rail|Newark Light Rail]], [[North Jersey Coast Line]], [[Northeast Corridor Line]], [[Raritan Valley Line]]<br>'''[[PATH (rail system)|PATH]]:''' [[Newark\u2013World Trade Center]]<br>'''[[Coach USA]]'''\n|-\n| [[Iselin, New Jersey|Iselin]]||{{amtk|Metropark}}||'''[[Amtrak]]:''' {{lnl|Amtrak|Northeast Regional}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Keystone Service}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Vermonter}}<br>'''[[NJ Transit Rail Operations|NJ Transit]]:''' [[Northeast Corridor Line]]\n|-\n| [[Trenton, New Jersey|Trenton]]||{{amtk|Trenton}}||'''[[Amtrak]]:''' {{lnl|Amtrak|Northeast Regional}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Cardinal}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Carolinian}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Crescent}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Keystone Service}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Palmetto}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Pennsylvanian}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Silver Star}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Silver Meteor}}, {{lnl|Amtrak|Vermonter}}<br>